    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out under the MRL 2 assessment matrix. Uncertainty quantification confirms the RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied at the 97.5th percentile of the input uncertainty space. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the defined context of use.",
